    <item>
      <title>舒默（Schumer</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/schumer-leads-party-at-odds-with-itself-after-shutdown-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院民主党领导人查克·舒默（Chuck Schumer）的呼吁避免了破坏性的政府关闭，这使唐纳德·特朗普总统的政策疏远了政治基础，并对党长老的谨慎回应感到沮丧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/schumer-leads-party-at-odds-with-itself-after-shutdown-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Magyar Upstages Orban表示改变匈牙利政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/orban-and-magyar-hold-dueling-rallies-to-sway-hungarian-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利反对派领导人彼得·玛格尔（Peter Magyar）在决斗集会上超过了总理维克多·奥班（Viktor Orban），这突显了选举前一年的政治景观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/orban-and-magyar-hold-dueling-rallies-to-sway-hungarian-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 08:24:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国敦促对俄罗斯的压力，如果普京在乌克兰休战中巴尔克斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/uk-urges-economic-pressure-on-russia-if-putin-balks-at-truce</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）呼吁西方国家加大对弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）的压力，称俄罗斯总统“迟早”将不得不就乌克兰的停火进行认真的讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/uk-urges-economic-pressure-on-russia-if-putin-balks-at-truce</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
